# Web Conventions

- `apps/web` is a Next.js app-router frontend.
- Route files live under `apps/web/src/app`.
- Shared frontend utilities live under `apps/web/src/lib`.

- When editing frontend code:
- prefer app-router patterns already used in `src/app`
- keep presentation concerns in the web app instead of moving them into API or DB packages
- introduce shared utilities only when reuse is clear

- Default to matching the existing React, Next.js, and Tailwind-style patterns already present in the app.
